{
  "stem": "27409.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were a sect from Bessarabia-- from Bessarabia which were specialized in [INAUDIBLE] work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They had there [INAUDIBLE] took these carriages [COUGHS], pardon, the peat away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there were beatings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They had there Romanian veteran war, I couldn't [INAUDIBLE] them, the invalid's, which were from the front, which were mostly Iron Guards.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Jews-- [INAUDIBLE] they had pieces of rubber pipe, some filled with iron-- they were beating.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I had to work forwards, forwards, and German came only in inspection.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The head of the camp was Romanian Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was from Transylvania, Lekatosz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was a beast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He enjoyed beating.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then, we had particular I remember, it was a Romanian officer, which-- which lost an eye on the front, which hated Jewish women.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he was beating them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I will tell you afterwards why I remember him so well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I worked there first in digging.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We were given, in the morning, a bit of hot water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Noon time, they recorded pea broth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I heard afterwards-- I didn't realize at the time-- they were poisoned peas, peas and beans we had.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And a piece pea polenta-- from peas made.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They were really trying to see how long you could survive with this food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I worked from June up to end of September in the turf-- a peat exploitation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Then one of the Romanian supervisor was a student in mining engineering, needed tutoring in mathematics.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I don't know how he got to know that I am mathematician.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So he asked me if I want-- he wants tutoring.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Today he took me off two hours or three hours to tutor him in mathematics.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "What I got out from this was three hours less work under these inhuman conditions.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
